ITV Tour De France 2012 Stage 11 Highlights PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen. Stage 11, Albertville to La Toussuire-Les Sybelles. A short, explosive major mountain stage today only 148 km long although about half of them are uphill. The stage finishes at altitude in La Toussuire after an 18-km climb. None of the contenders can afford to lose time today.
